                                    El acuerdo de el valor de la propiedad es por este medio que el embarcador o el agente del embarcador firmando en su nombre declara especificamente el
                                    valor de este no excediendo $5,000 por animal. A no ser que se especifique de orta manera en el documento.
                                </span>
                                Shipper is encouraged to obtain it’s own insurance, it being acknowledged and understood animals transported may
                                have an actual value in excess of the Agreed Value. Carrier does not provide insurance for Shipper’s goods. Carrier assumes the liability of a common carrier subject to to the provisions of 49 U.S.C. 14706.
                            </p>
                        </div>

                    </div>

                    <div class="row">
                        <div class="col-md-4">
                            <div class="form-group">
                                <label class="text-bold">Ship To</label>
                                <input type="text" class="form-control" required name="Date" value="@Model.ShipTo" readonly>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-md-4">
                            <div class="form-group">
                                <label class="text-bold">Barn#</label>
                                <input type="text" class="form-control" required name="Date" value="@Model.BarnTo" readonly>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-md-4">
                            <div class="form-group">
                                <label class="text-bold">Phone</label>
                                <input type="text" class="form-control" required name="Date" value="@Model.ToPhoneNumber" readonly>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="row">
                        <div class="col-md-6">
                            <div class="form-group">
                                <label class="text-bold">Address</label>
                                <input type="text" class="form-control" required name="Date" value="@Model.AddressTo" readonly>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <div class="col-md-6">
                            <div class="form-group">
                                <label class="text-bold">City And State</label>
                                <input type="text" class="form-control" required name="Date" value="@Model.ToCityAndState" readonly>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="row">
                        <div class="col-md-12">
                            <table class="table">
                                <thead>
                                    <tr>
                                        <th style="width:30%">BILL TO: NAME AND ADDRESS</th>
                                        <th style="width:35%">
                                            NAME, NUMBER, DESCRIPTION
                                            KIND OF ANIMALS.
                                            PARAPHERNALIA, PETS, MASCOTS, ETC.
                                        </th>
                                        <th>
                                            Maximum Agreed VALUE OF EACH ANIMAL

                                        </th>
                                        <th>
                                            CHARGES FOR EXCESS VALUE

                                        </th>
                                        <th>
                                            BASIC CHARGE
                                            PER ANIMAL
                                        </th>

                                    </tr>
                                </thead>
                                <tbody style="background-color:#f6faff">
                                    <!-- Rows -->
                                    @foreach (var item in Model.billToRecords)
                                    {
                                        <tr>
                                            <td>@item.Name, @item.Address</td>
                                            <td>@item.Description</td>
                                            <td>@item.AgreedValue</td>
                                            <td>@item.ChargeValue</td>
                                            <td>@item.ChargePerAnimal</td>

                                        </tr>

                                        basicCharges += @item.ChargePerAnimal.Value;
                                        chargesForExcessValue += @item.ChargeValue.Value;
                                    }

                                </tbody>
                            </table>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="row custom-border">
                        <div class="col-md-5 ">
                            <div class="form-group">
                                <label class="text-bold" style="display: inline-block;">By:</label>
                                <input type="text" class="form-control" required name="By" value="@Model.By" placeholder="N/A" readonly style="display: inline-block; width: calc(100% - 60px);"><br />

                                <label class="text-bold" style="display: inline-block;">Date:</label>
                                <input type="text" class="form-control" style="display: inline-block; width: calc(100% - 70px);" required name="ReceivingDate" value="@Model.ReceivingDate" placeholder="N/A" readonly><br />

                                <p>If COLORS, REGISTRATION or TACK sent with horses receiver must acknowledge receipt.</p><br />

                                <label class="text-bold" style="display: inline-block;">Received By:</label>
                                <input type="text" class="form-control" style="display: inline-block; width: calc(100% - 120px);" required name="ReceivedBy" value="@Model.ReceivedBy" placeholder="N/A" readonly>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-md-3 ">
                            <div class="form-group">
                                <label class="text-bold" style="display: inline-block;">Payment Type</label>
                                <input type="text" class="form-control" name="PaymentType" value="@Model.PaymentType" readonly style="display: inline-block; width: 55%;"><br />

                                <label class="text-bold" style="display: inline-block;">Payment$</label>
                                <input type="text" class="form-control" style="display: inline-block; width:67%;" name="Payment" value="@Model.Payment" readonly><br />

                                <label class="text-bold" style="display: inline-block;">Date</label>
                                <input type="text" class="form-control" style="display: inline-block; width: 83%;" name="PaymentDate" value="@Model.PaymentDate" readonly><br />

                                <label class="text-bold" style="display: inline-block;">By</label>
                                <input type="text" class="form-control" style="display: inline-block; width:90%;" name="PaymentBy" value="@Model.PaymentBy" readonly><br />

                                <label class="text-bold" style="display: inline-block;">Check#</label>
                                <input type="text" class="form-control" style="display: inline-block; width: 75%;" name="Check" value="@Model.Check" readonly>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-md-4">
                            <div class="form-group">
                                <div class="input-row">
                                    <label class="text-bold" style="display: inline-block; width: 160px;">Basic Charges</label>
                                    <input type="text" class="form-control" name="BasicCharges" value="@Model.BasicCharges" readonly style="display: inline-block; width: 115px;">
                                </div>
                                <div class="input-row">
                                    <label class="text-bold" style="display: inline-block; width: 160px;">Charges For Excess Value</label>
                                    <input type="text" class="form-control" name="ChargesForExcessValue" value="@Model.ChargesForExcessValue" readonly style="display: inline-block; width: 115px;">
                                </div>
                                <div class="input-row">
                                    <label class="text-bold" style="display: inline-block; width: 160px;">Lay Overs</label>
                                    <input type="text" class="form-control" name="Layovers" value="@Model.Layovers" readonly style="display: inline-block; width: 115px;">
                                </div>
                                <div class="input-row">
                                    <label class="text-bold" style="display: inline-block; width: 160px;">Vet Fees</label>
                                    <input type="text" class="form-control" name="VetFees" value="@Model.VetFees" readonly style="display: inline-block; width: 115px;">
                                </div>
                                <div class="input-row">
                                    <label class="text-bold" style="display: inline-block; width: 160px;">Other</label>
                                    <input type="text" class="form-control" name="Other" value="@Model.Other" readonly style="display: inline-block; width: 115px;">
                                </div>
                                <div class="input-row">
                                    <label class="text-bold" style="display: inline-block; width: 160px;">Total Charges</label>
                                    <input type="text" class="form-control" name="TotalCharges" value="@Model.TotalCharges" readonly style="display: inline-block; width: 115px;">
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>

