                                <b>SECTION 3:</b>

                                A copy of Carrier’s Terms and Conditions of Shipment, a document separate from this bill of lading’s Contract Terms and Conditions, may be obtained from Carrier’s
                                address identified above. SHIPPER ACKNOWLEDGES IT HAS OBTAINED AND READ A COPY OF CARRIER’S TERMS AND CONDITIONS OF SHIPMENT OR THAT IT HAS BEEN
                                OFFERED AND HAS DECLINED THE OPPORTUNITY TO DO SO, BUT IN ANY EVENT SHIPPER ACCEPTS AND AGREES TO BE BOUND BY THE PROVISIONS OF SAID
                                TERMS AND CONDITIONS OF SHIPMENT.
                            </p><br />
                        </div>
                    </div>

                </div>

            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>










